item.title: Cache Trouble
item.dc:creator: @sinisoul sini
item.description:
@sinisoul wrote:

Errors from program would be nice. You have to remember that unlike the file information tables, specific files from a file index may not be backwards compatible when you have a large margin between revisions. Some of the information is junk and not needed but I can guarantee when you are writing/reading they will almost never load correctly.
